@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xwhvcg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.54) * wp.abs(v1 + 0.35)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v1) - wp.abs(v1))
    tmp = (0.95 * (v0 * (v2 + 0.39 - v0 + 0.74)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.78 / v2 + 0.41)) / ((v1 + 0.02 - v1 + 0.35) * (v2 + 0.39 - v2 + 0.12)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v2)
    v0 = wp.sin((v2 / (v1 + 0.03 + tmp + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
